      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ce7829c73576d78b623b10e"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Agreed. I doubt the <i>[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHysteria],Hysteria]]</i> would be certifiable for civilian travel in the Inner Sphere, most likely they would strip it for spare parts because of the potential safety hazards.\n\nYesterday, climate control broke again during maneuvers and our cabin became an oven while I was sleeping... I wish we could have a proper DropShip.",
      "branches": [
