    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0c001ccfad9f48958815ad"
      },
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Sumire, both of them have a point... me and the rest of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMechTechs],MechTech]] could definitely use some extra room plus not having to constantly jerry rigging systems or components might give me more time to work on prepping 'Mechs to action.",
      "branches": [
