    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c48e5b31bc1f5898782f39f"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "The <i>Hysteria</i> might be slightly worn out by all these decades of service with [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreMarkhamsMarauders],Markham's Marauders]] and before them but...",
      "branches": [
        {
