    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cd6fc6a86176b9236ca862e"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Decades??? \n\nDarius, some of the oldest parts still have the manufacture dates of the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreTerranHegemony],Terran Hegemony]] companies that produced them. ",
      "branches": [
        {
