      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c134a56f29b0cb14e99e4d0"
      },
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Mr. Oliveira, that's also something I plan to discuss with Kamea when the games are over because we're going to need extra firepower when we return to the Reach to help the [[DM.Factions[faction_AuriganRestoration],Restoration]].\n\n",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 10,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c65e3ce44cc9d067321b359"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
