    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c4b3a5437c12451063f5196"
      },
      "index": 12,
      "text": "And finally the most important item of this meeting's agenda: tonight's games and I'm informing that a viewing screen is being set on the mess hall, with food and drinks for everyone.\n\nNo betting pool this time - no one is betting against the captain inside this ship on my watch.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 13,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
          "onlyOnce": false,
          "idRef": {
            "id": "9c8f711ec572fdceec1d629a"
          },
          "inputBypass": false,
          "auxiliaryLink": false,
          "comment": ""
        }
      ],
      "nodeType": 1,
      "truthValue": false,
      "autoFollowBranchDelay": 1,
