      "idRef": {
        "id": "9ce5a470a0a3c088ad907de1"
      },
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The games became politics the moment Kamea announced her claim to the Aurigan throne after her initial victory.\n\nI'm her personal friend and an Aurigan and yesterday's crew meeting made it very clear that we know the odds of following her and we're willing to risk them.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
